<br><br>

<span style="font-weight: bold">2015 January 20:  New early-morning aikido class at Makati Sports</span><br>
<span style="line-height: 22px; font-size: 20px; color: red;">(THIS EVENT IS CONCLUDED. ALL MATERIALS RELATING TO IT ARE RETAINED FOR ARCHIVING PURPOSES ONLY.)</span><br><br><br>

The Makati Aikido Club inaugurated a new early-morning aikido class on Tuesday, 2015 January 20th, at its dojo in Makati Sports. The instructor is Giovanni Capannelli, 5th dan Aikikai.<br><br>

With this new morning class, the MAC's class offerings have now grown to seven adult classes per week and two youngsters classes per week. <a href="../trainingsched/dojos.php" target="_blank"><u>Click here for the updated training schedule</u>.</a><br><br>

